{
  "texts": [
    "To validate the OED Framework, we executed the BERTopic framework on two datasets, Banking77_eng and Banking77_vni.",
    "The clustering results in Cases 1 and 2 demonstrate the superior performance of the BERTopic framework with the English dataset, where 73 intents were identified, closely aligning with the 77 predetermined categories.",
    "However, in the Banking77_vni dataset, the count of identified intents notably decreased to 65.",
    "In Case 3, the OED Framework exhibited better performance with the Banking77_vni dataset compared to the BERTopic framework for the Vietnamese language, yielding 76 extracted intents.",
    "Subsequently, we applied the OED Framework to the HCMUT_FAQ_vni dataset (Case 4), resulting in a total of 284 clusters with significant noised clusters, and duplicated clusters."
  ]
}